title: GTA Online: A Safehouse in the Hills
headline: GTA Online: A Safehouse in the Hills
subtitle: New Vinewood Club Benefits For GTA+ Members
content:
GTA+ Members can now get exclusive access to The Vinewood Club Garage Workshop features at the Mansion Vehicle Workshop, including drift kits, Hao’s Special Works, and Benny’s Original Motor Works upgrades.

Remotely manage staff members at the Smuggler Hangar, Cargo Warehouses, and Bail Office — without having to visit the business in person — right on the Vinewood Club App.
